[21:45.59]	Make me not sighted like the basilisk:
[21:48.61]	I have look'd on thousands, who have sped the better
[21:52.58]	By my regard, but kill'd none so. Camillo,--
[21:55.74]	As you are certainly a gentleman, thereto
[21:58.96]	Clerk-like experienced, which no less adorns
[22:02.39]	Our gentry than our parents' noble names,
[22:05.54]	In whose success we are gentle,--I beseech you,
