[22:19.46]POLIXENES	A sickness caught of me, and yet I well!
[22:22.54]	I must be answer'd. Dost thou hear, Camillo,
[22:25.83]	I conjure thee, by all the parts of man
[22:28.92]	Which honour does acknowledge, whereof the least
[22:32.62]	Is not this suit of mine, that thou declare
