[23:26.84]	To an infected jelly and my name
[23:29.52]	Be yoked with his that did betray the Best!
[23:32.88]	Turn then my freshest reputation to
[23:35.75]	A savour that may strike the dullest nostril
[23:39.25]	Where I arrive, and my approach be shunn'd,
[23:42.54]	Nay, hated too, worse than the great'st infection
[23:46.24]	That e'er was heard or read!
